{Possible Drops: Means the items that a Father can drop upon death.}

{Partner Skills: Partner Skills are the innate abilities each species of pals can have.}

{Work Suitability: Each Pal in Palworld is unique, with specific traits that make them better suited for particular tasks. These traits, known as Work Suitabilities, govern their efficiency in activities such as farming, mining, crafting, and more. Assigning the right Pal to the right task is essential for maximizing productivity and conserving resources.}

